refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;
mixedopenssl_pkcs7_verify stringfilename intflags stringoutfilename arraycainfo stringextracerts stringcontent stringp7bfilename
openssl_pkcs7_verify reads the S/MIME message contained in the given file and examines the digital signature.

&reftitle.notes;


  As specified in RFC 2045, lines may not be longer than 76 characters 
  in the filename parameter.
